to show what we can do, eh?

257
00:22:37.723 --> 00:22:39.414
- Oh, indeed.
- Really?

258
00:22:40.027 --> 00:22:41.937
Like me. I can be a wheel.

259
00:22:42.651 --> 00:22:43.666
Hmm.

260
00:22:44.700 --> 00:22:47.319
Perfect. That's my chance.

261
00:23:42.115 --> 00:23:46.425
Okay, everybody, turn!
Ready for the base coat over here!

262
00:23:56.644 --> 00:24:01.347
Splendid, splendid. Stack those neatly,
plenty of time before the Queen arrives.

263
00:24:01.445 --> 00:24:02.590
It's the Queen!

264
00:24:02.693 --> 00:24:05.660
