Play, music fairies.

265
00:24:06.692 --> 00:24:07.937
Yes, play!

266
00:24:22.792 --> 00:24:24.482
Queen Clarion, Your Illustriousness!

267
00:24:24.583 --> 00:24:28.642
As Minister of Spring,
I welcome you to Springtime Square.

268
00:24:28.840 --> 00:24:31.142
What? No fireworks, Minister?

269
00:24:31.240 --> 00:24:34.142
Oh, well, yeah, that could be arranged.
Light fairies! Light fairies!

270
00:24:34.248 --> 00:24:37.315
I'm teasing.
You always make such a fuss,

271
00:24:37.416 --> 00:24:40.166
and everything always
turns out wonderfully.

272
00:24:43.049 --> 00:24:45.636
Well, I think you'll find
that we have things well in hand.

273
00:24:45.737 --> 00:24:47.231
When the Everblossom blooms,

274
00:24:47.338 --> 00:24:49.760
we'll be ready to bring
spring to the mainland!

275
00:24:49.866 --> 00:24:52.006
Music to my ears.

276
00:24:52.106 --> 00:24:55.205
I know you've all put in months
of practice and preparation,

277
00:24:55.723 --> 00:24:58.374
but keep up the good work
these last few days,

278
00:24:58.475 --> 00:25:00.418
- because just as fairies...
- Queen Clarion!

279
00:25:02.219 --> 00:25:03.178
Huh?

280
00:25:03.531 --> 00:25:04.938
Queen Clarion!

281
00:25:06.315 --> 00:25:08.520
- Did I miss anything?
- No, no, no.

282
00:25:08.684 --> 00:25:10.113
Phew! Good.

283
00:25:10.668 --> 00:25:11.627
It's all right.

284
00:25:11.724 --> 00:25:13.447
I came up with some fantastic things

285
00:25:13.548 --> 00:25:16.004
for tinkers to use
when we go to the mainland.

286
00:25:18.189 --> 00:25:19.596
What's she talking about?

287
00:25:19.694 --> 00:25:21.221
Let me show you!

288
00:25:22.862 --> 00:25:25.961
First, baby chipmunks
can't eat the whole nut, right?

289
00:25:26.061 --> 00:25:28.299
Their little teeth can't chew big bites.

290
00:25:28.398 --> 00:25:31.715
So you just crank back this lever,
and it's...

291
00:25:40.912 --> 00:25:42.025
Whoops.

292
00:25:42.320 --> 00:25:45.900
- It's kind of a work in progress.
- Yes, yes, yes. Very clever.

293
00:25:48.081 --> 00:25:49.041
Oh!

294
00:25:49.137 --> 00:25:51.626
And I made this, too.
It's a flower-sprayer.

295
00:25:51.730 --> 00:25:54.796
- Tinker Bell, I...
- Here, allow me to demonstrate.

296
00:26:04.211 --> 00:26:05.324
Sorry.

297
00:26:05.811 --> 00:26:09.521
