300
00:26:15.252 --> 00:26:18.002
Tinker fairies
don't go to the mainland, dear.

301
00:26:18.261 --> 00:26:19.220
What?

302
00:26:19.284 --> 00:26:22.732
All of those things
are done by the nature-talent fairies.

303
00:26:22.836 --> 00:26:25.325
Your work is here in Pixie Hollow.

304
00:26:25.844 --> 00:26:28.911
