- I'm sorry, Tinker Bell.

305
00:26:31.221 --> 00:26:34.867
Oh, okay. No. No, that's good.

306
00:26:34.966 --> 00:26:37.552
I mean,
I really couldn't make it anyway.

307
00:26:37.655 --> 00:26:42.325
So, good. Yeah.
This actually works out good.

308
00:26:42.808 --> 00:26:47.347
I mean, well...
So, I'm just gonna... Yeah.

309
00:27:04.089 --> 00:27:05.464
Back so soon?

310
00:27:06.138 --> 00:27:07.282
You didn't go?

311
00:27:07.385 --> 00:27:10.833
Goodness, no.
Far too much work to do down here.

312
00:27:20.412 --> 00:27:23.511
Vidia was right. Being a tinker stinks.

313
00:27:24.348 --> 00:27:26.072
Excuse me?

314
00:27:26.812 --> 00:27:29.879
It's just, why don't we get to go
to the mainland?

315
00:27:30.940 --> 00:27:35.097
The mainland? Who gives
a pile of pebbles about the mainland?

316
00:27:35.774 --> 00:27:38.196
But, Fairy Mary,
the other fairies get to go.

317
00:27:38.302 --> 00:27:41.369
Now, Tinker Bell,
are you a garden fairy?

318
00:27:42.239 --> 00:27:43.383
Well, no.

319
00:27:43.486 --> 00:27:45.820
- Are you a light fairy?
- No.

320
00:27:45.918 --> 00:27:48.569
Animal fairy? Water fairy, perhaps?

321
00:27:48.669 --> 00:27:50.077
No and no.

322
00:27:50.174 --> 00:27:54.201
No. You're not. You are a tinker.
It's who you are.

323
00:27:54.624 --> 00:27:56.053
Be proud of it.

324
00:27:57.376 --> 00:28:00.223
The day you can
magically make the flowers grow,

325
00:28:00.320 --> 00:28:03.964
or capture the rays of the sun
and whatnot, then you can go.

326
00:28:04.321 --> 00:28:06.459
Until then, your work is here.

327
00:28:30.339 --> 00:28:32.413
Good idea, Fairy Mary.

328
00:28:43.269 --> 00:28:44.227
Get your pixie dust yet?

329
00:28:44.292 --> 00:28:45.252
Just did.

330
00:28:45.316 --> 00:28:47.105
- Nice day for flying.
- Sure is.

331
00:28:47.204 --> 00:28:48.164
Here you go, Silvermist.

332
00:28:48.261 --> 00:28:49.919
Thank you, Terence.

333
00:28:51.525 --> 00:28:53.380
I hope Tinker Bell is okay.

334
00:28:53.478 --> 00:28:55.747
I know. That poor little sapling.

335
00:28:56.550 --> 00:28:58.525
