336
00:28:58.631 --> 00:29:00.899
Well, I wouldn't blame her
if she stayed in bed all day.

337
00:29:00.998 --> 00:29:02.460
Morning, girls!

338
00:29:02.567 --> 00:29:03.568
- Tinker Bell?
- Tinker Bell?

339
00:29:03.591 --> 00:29:07.334
Guess what? I've decided I'm not
gonna be a tinker fairy anymore.

340
00:29:07.432 --> 00:29:08.391
- What?
- What?

341
00:29:08.488 --> 00:29:11.522
Well, I was thinking.
Why do I have to be a tinker?

342
00:29:11.624 --> 00:29:14.080
Just 'cause
some silly hammer glowed?

343
00:29:14.184 --> 00:29:16.738
I mean, who's to say
it wasn't some big mistake?

344
00:29:16.841 --> 00:29:19.045
Maybe I can just switch my talent.

345
00:29:19.146 --> 00:29:22.407
