417
00:33:47.143 --> 00:33:51.334
Okay, what can I teach you that's
gonna do the least amount of damage?

418
00:33:53.768 --> 00:33:56.189
Oh, I know. Follow me, Tinker Bell.

419
00:34:01.449 --> 00:34:05.475
The last light of day,
it's the richest kind of all!

420
00:34:05.578 --> 00:34:09.287
Wait for it. Wait for it.

421
00:34:09.385 --> 00:34:11.174
Okay, and now!

422
00:34:11.273 --> 00:34:13.063
Oh, wow.

423
00:34:15.337 --> 00:34:16.385
