- No. It's light.

427
00:34:37.197 --> 00:34:38.506
Okay, okay.

428
00:35:09.520 --> 00:35:10.535
Stay.

429
00:35:10.640 --> 00:35:13.543
- Here, Tink. Let me...
- No! I almost got it.

430
00:35:13.648 --> 00:35:15.274
