433
00:35:27.666 --> 00:35:28.877
Oh, no.

434
00:35:29.555 --> 00:35:31.214
Whoa!

435
00:35:34.356 --> 00:35:36.244
I wonder how it's going.

436
00:35:37.076 --> 00:35:38.864
Fly, Tink, fly!

437
00:35:39.508 --> 00:35:40.621
Uh-oh.

438
00:35:42.004 --> 00:35:43.019
We'll save you, Tink!

439
00:35:43.125 --> 00:35:45.012
Bob and weave!
Bob and weave!

440
00:35:45.109 --> 00:35:47.248
Cover your tushy!

441
00:35:59.702 --> 00:36:01.938
- We fiddle and fix.
- Craft and create.

442
00:36:02.038 --> 00:36:04.079
- Carve acorn buckets.
- To hold flower paint.

443
00:36:04.182 --> 00:36:06.638
- Preparing for spring.
- We do all this and more.

444
00:36:06.743 --> 00:36:10.355
- Yes, being a tinker is never a bore!
- Yes, being a tinker is never a bore!

445
00:36:12.696 --> 00:36:14.834
Tinker Bell,
I'd like a word with you.

446
00:36:14.937 --> 00:36:16.245
Fairy Mary!

447
00:36:16.888 --> 00:36:21.395
See, I was on my deliveries,
and it's actually kind of...

448
00:36:21.497 --> 00:36:24.629
